Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--------------------------------------------------Avant--------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我話說在前面 瀧老師是很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不允許你們小瞧他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟 我們的目標是全國大會啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--------------------------------------------------Part A--------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你這水平都和男生差不多了 怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是大號手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在吹奏樂的樂器中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,葉月吹的大號是特別需要肺活量的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以前輩一直都在訓練我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,吹到沒氣也要繼續吹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,再吹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,別停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,還能再吹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,還能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,還能吹更久的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,全部吹出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一口氣不剩吹出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,吹吹吹吹出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,於是每天都努力練到耳朵變紅的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,吹奏樂部真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}真嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,和去年比胸圍一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,進入春天後 難道不應該豐滿起來徹底長大成人的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:50.35,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W6\c&HA1FCFD&\bord1\shad1\pos(200,74)}朝思暮想的C-Cup
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 小綠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,終於結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,飛機場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你們倆 這麼委婉地鼓勵我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我差點覺得心都要碎了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是明日香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 體檢結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有長大一點嗎 小姑娘們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:27.10,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(760,480)\fad(500,0)\blur2}Festival 我 們 來 了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 現在開始發下周正式演出的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,請按順序過來領取
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,首先從打擊樂小組開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,堺同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,蒲江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在Sunrise Festival——俗稱SunFes上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,作為音樂活動的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,每次都會由府內各學校的吹奏樂部進行遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來 低音部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}這裡這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這種演奏方式在吹奏樂部中叫做行進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有像這次這樣列隊行進演奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也有邊變換隊形邊進行演奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在對行進演奏比賽下功夫的名校裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎還有因為憧憬其演出服裝而決定就讀學校的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今天因為操場沒人用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的練習會在外面進行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,試穿完衣服後就換上運動服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,到操場集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼女生就在音樂教室…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣 合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 綠也想抱著低音提琴參加行進啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,沒可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這次就混在我們初學者隊伍裡一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐太可愛了 簡直如天使一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,待會兒可以一起拍張照嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可以是可以 去年不是也拍了嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦 無論拍幾次都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是香織 的確很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 明日香才更帥氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,身材又好 人又漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子 難道說會被曬黑？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只有露出來的部分被曬出痕跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,用這個防曬霜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵…學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,被久美子叫學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大家聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我們先不拿樂器練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一年級的初學者進行舞步練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其他所有人則從行進練習開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果腳步不齊 某種程度上來說會比吹錯更顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,請大家集中注意力好好練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,前進一步的距離是62.5厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,先邁左腳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一步62.5厘米等同於八步五米
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須一邊演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊不看腳下 保持這個步幅前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果走得好 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒走好 則是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,注意踏齊步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,身子有些搖晃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看前方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,把身子挺直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 那邊 沒對齊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好 休息五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,終於能休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,正式演出時會更熱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 小綠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好像因為她比較可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以讓她去當護旗手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,護旗手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是聖女出身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 像我連迷之舞步都還沒掌握呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那個北宇治特有的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是迷之舞步 實在太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊往前走 嗯…像這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣…這樣…這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣…這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 好像是這樣來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,的確是迷之舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛還被明日香學姐訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,0)\fnHiragino Sans GB W6\shad0\c&H565958&\pos(306,201)}喂！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,0)\fnHiragino Sans GB W6\shad0\c&H565958&\pos(306,317)\frz357}你到底
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,0)\fnHiragino Sans GB W6\shad0\c&H565958&\frz4.8\pos(341,418)}有沒有幹勁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,0)\fnHiragino Sans GB W6\shad0\c&H565958&\frz355\pos(965,204)}不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,0)\fnHiragino Sans GB W6\shad0\c&H565958&\pos(1015,334)\frz7.4}慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,0)\fnHiragino Sans GB W6\shad0\c&H565958&\pos(896,481)\frz353}還是慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,吶 覺不覺得明日香學姐比部長還嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明日香學姐是指揮嘛
